arStrings.szText: (PH) {c_important}Raptor Strike{/c} increases your Lucky Hit Chance against an enemy hit by {c_number}[{SF_15}*100|%x|]{/c} for {c_number}{SF_16}{/c} seconds.
(PH) {c_important}Raptor Strike{/c} makes enemies hit {c_important}{u}Vulnerable{/u}{/c} for {c_number}{SF_17}{/c} seconds if there are fewer than {c_number}[{SF_18}]{/c} others Close to them.
(PH) Hitting a Distant enemy with {c_important}Raptor Strike{/c} Pulls them Close to you and Knocks them Down for {c_number}{buffduration:KNOCKDOWN}{/c} seconds.
